This task is the <span class="rosetta__text--italic">opposite</span> of the [[PPM conversion through a pipe]]. In this task, using a delegate tool (like <span class="rosetta__text--bold">cjpeg</span>, one of the netpbm package, or <span class="rosetta__text--bold">convert</span> of the ImageMagick package) we read an image file and load it into the data storage type [[Basic bitmap storage" title="Category:Input Output]]

